---
source: crates/ship-policy/src/help.rs
expression: "short_hint(AgentRole::Captain, Some(TaskPhase::ReviewPending))"
---
Available actions:
- `captain_steer` — Send course-correction to the mate
- `captain_merge` — Accept the mate's work and merge
- `captain_cancel` — Cancel the current task
- `captain_review_diff` — See the diff of the mate's work
- `captain_git_status` — Check git status of the session worktree
- `captain_rebase_status` — Check the state of an in-progress rebase
- `code` — Read, search, edit files, run commands, commit
- `web_search` — Search the web
